title: SAVE THE DATE - May 3-5, 2016 8th Circuit Judicial Conference (United States Court of ...
text: (Source: United States Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit) The judges of the Eighth Circuit invite you to attend the 2016 Eighth Circuit Judicial Conference at the Embassy Suites Hotel in Rogers, Arkansas. The conference will take place May 3-5, 2016.
